      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="组件间通讯"><a href="#组件间通讯" class="headerlink" title="组件间通讯"></a>组件间通讯</h2><h3 id="父向子组件通讯"><a href="#父向子组件通讯" class="headerlink" title="父向子组件通讯"></a>父向子组件通讯</h3><pre><code>利用`props`</code></pre><h3 id="子向父组件通讯"><a href="#子向父组件通讯" class="headerlink" title="子向父组件通讯"></a>子向父组件通讯</h3><pre><code>利用 `$emit`子组件触发父组件的事件来实现对父组件通讯`$emit` 同时可以抛出一个值,父组件可以利用`$event`访问到该值</code></pre><ul><li>正常组件间的通讯 </li><li>利用<code>v-model</code>进行表单间的通讯 —- 例如搜索组件,需要将组件内<code>&lt;input/&gt;</code>的值传递给 父组件</li><li>利用<code>$refs</code>父组件来触发子组件的事件来实现对父组件通讯</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 父组件</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;h1&gt;这是父组件&lt;<span class="regexp">/h1&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">    &lt;p v-if="show"&gt;show message&lt;/</span>p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;childButton v-on:showHideMsg=<span class="string">"showHideMsg"</span> :text=<span class="string">"text1"</span>&gt;&lt;/childButton&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;childButton v-on:showHideMsg=<span class="string">"show=$event"</span> :text=<span class="string">"text2"</span>&gt;&lt;/childButton&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;CustomInput v-model=<span class="string">"output"</span>&gt;&lt;/CustomInput&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div&gt;&#123;&#123; <span class="string">`父组件获取子组件input输入框内容: <span class="subst">$&#123;output&#125;</span>`</span> &#125;&#125;&lt;<span class="regexp">/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">    &lt;br/</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;Child ref=<span class="string">"child"</span>&gt;&lt;/Child&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;button type=<span class="string">"button"</span> name=<span class="string">"button"</span> @click=<span class="string">"getChildMsg"</span>&gt;click&lt;<span class="regexp">/button&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">    &lt;p&gt;&#123;&#123; `父组件获取到的值$&#123;childMsg&#125;` &#125;&#125;&lt;/</span>p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;<span class="regexp">/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">&lt;/</span>template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> childButton <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'./childButton.vue'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> CustomInput <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'./input.vue'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> Child <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'./child.vue'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    name: <span class="string">'parent'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    components: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        childButton, CustomInput, Child</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    data () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            output: <span class="string">''</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            show: <span class="literal">true</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            text1: <span class="string">'切换'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            text2: <span class="string">'隐藏'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            childMsg: <span class="string">''</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    methods: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        showHideMsg (name) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">this</span>.show = !<span class="keyword">this</span>.show</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        getChildMsg () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">this</span>.childMsg = <span class="keyword">this</span>.$refs.child.childEvent()</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/script&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//子组件-$emit</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;template lang=<span class="string">"html"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;p&gt;这是子组件- $emit &lt;<span class="regexp">/p&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">    &lt;button type="button" name="button" @click="$emit('showHideMsg',false)"&gt;&#123;&#123;text&#125;&#125;&lt;/</span>button&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;<span class="regexp">/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">&lt;/</span>template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    props: [<span class="string">'show'</span>, <span class="string">'text'</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    data () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/script&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//子组件-表单</span><br><span class="line">/**</span><br><span class="line">* 组件内的 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span>&gt;</span> 必须：</span><br><span class="line">* 将其 value 特性绑定到一个名叫 value 的 prop 上</span><br><span class="line">* 在其 input 事件被触发时，将新的值通过自定义的 input 事件抛出</span><br><span class="line">*/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">template</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"html"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>这是子组件- input <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">:value</span>=<span class="string">"value"</span> <span class="attr">v-on:input</span>=<span class="string">"$emit('input', $event.target.value)"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">template</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    props: [<span class="string">'value'</span>],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">    data () &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//子组件-$refs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">template</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"html"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>子组件,<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>子组件消息<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">""</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">""</span> <span class="attr">v-model</span>=<span class="string">'childMsg'</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>&#123;&#123; `子组件中input: $&#123;childMsg&#125;` &#125;&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">template</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">    data () &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">            childMsg: <span class="string">''</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">    methods: &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">        childEvent () &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">this</span>.childMsg</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="非父子组件间通讯"><a href="#非父子组件间通讯" class="headerlink" title="非父子组件间通讯"></a>非父子组件间通讯</h3><ul><li>利用events hus进行通讯</li></ul><p>官方demo : [<a href="https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/guide/migration.html#dispatch-%E5%92%8C-broadcast-%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><code>$dispatch</code> 和 <code>$broadcast</code> 替换 </a><br>通过实例化一个空的 <code>Vue</code> 实例来实现了一个事件分发接口 </p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 1. 实例化新的Vue对象</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> Vue <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'vue'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> Vue()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 2. 利用插件 注册到全局Vue中</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> eventsHub = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    install (Vue, options) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Vue.prototype.$hub = <span class="keyword">new</span> Vue()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Vue.use(eventsHub);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在组件中，可以使用 <code>$emit</code>, <code>$on</code>, <code>$off</code> 分别来分发、监听、取消监听事件： </p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 分发组件 */</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">methods: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    todo: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) </sp